BBEX3.D.NGN.EUR.CA.AC.000: Exchange rates for the euro in Nigeria / EUR 1 = NGN ... (middle)

General: Until December 1998, listed in D-Mark; see wt6180/81 (official exchange rates) and wt6192/93 (free market rates). On 1 January 1999, the multiple exchange rate system was unified on the basis of the free market rate.
Source: Calculated on the basis of buying and selling rates of the Central Bank of Nigeria, Abuja.
